	(17, 'sc', 6, 'Set your own Goal!', 4, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
	(18, 'en', 7, 'Goal 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Use a pedometer and aim to take 10,000 steps a day. Start slowly and build up to the 10,000. Week one: Aim for 5,000 steps per day. Week two: Aim for 7,000 steps. Week three: Aim to hit 10,000 steps per day. You can buy a pedometer in most chemists and sports supply shops at a reasonable price.</li>\r\n	<li>(A pedometer is a device, usually portable, that counts each step a person takes by detecting the movement of the person&rsquo;s hips)</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(18, 'fr', 7, 'Objectif 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Utilisez un podom&egrave;tre et essayez de faire 10.000 pas par jour. Commencez doucement et augmentez jusqu&rsquo;aux 10.000. Semaine 1&nbsp;: visez 5.000 pas par jour. Semaine 2&nbsp;: visez 7.000 pas. Semaine 3&nbsp;: visez 10.000 pas par jour. Vous pouvez acheter un podom&egrave;tre dans la plupart des boutiques de sport &agrave; un prix raisonnable.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n   <li>(un podom&egrave;tre est un dispositif, g&eacute;n&eacute;ralement portable, qui compte le nombre de pas qu&rsquo;une personne effectue en d&eacute;tectant le mouvement de ses hanches)</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(18, 'sc', 7, 'Goal 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Use a pedometer and aim to take 10,000 steps a day. Start slowly and build up to the 10,000. Week one: Aim for 5,000 steps per day. Week two: Aim for 7,000 steps. Week three: Aim to hit 10,000 steps per day. You can buy a pedometer in most chemists and sports supply shops at a reasonable price.</li>\r\n	<li>(A pedometer is a device, usually portable, that counts each step a person takes by detecting the movement of the person&rsquo;s hips)</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(19, 'en', 7, 'Goal 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Eat more fruit and vegetables. Make sure you have at least five portions per day. A portion of vegetables is three heaped tablespoons and a portion of fruit is a regular size apple, a banana, or two small plums or mandarin oranges.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(19, 'fr', 7, 'Objectif 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Mangez plus de fruits et l&eacute;gumes. Assurez-vous d&rsquo;en prendre au moins 5 portions par jour. Une portion de l&eacute;gumes correspond &agrave; 3 cuill&egrave;res &agrave; soupe remplis, et une porte de fruit correspond &agrave; une pomme de taille normale, une banane, ou 2 petites prunes ou mandarines.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(19, 'sc', 7, 'Goal 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Eat more fruit and vegetables. Make sure you have at least five portions per day. A portion of vegetables is three heaped tablespoons and a portion of fruit is a regular size apple, a banana, or two small plums or mandarin oranges.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(20, 'en', 7, 'Goal 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Go for a 20-minute walk four times a week. Start at a pace that is comfortable for you. Take a few weeks to build up to a faster pace &ndash; enough to get your heart beating faster than normal.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(20, 'fr', 7, 'Objectif 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Faites une marche de 20 minutes, 4 fois par semaine. Commencez &agrave; un rythme confortable pour vous. Prenez quelques semaines pour atteindre un rythme plus rapide &ndash; suffisamment pour que votre c&oelig;ur batte plus vite que d&rsquo;habitude.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(20, 'sc', 7, 'Goal 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Go for a 20-minute walk four times a week. Start at a pace that is comfortable for you. Take a few weeks to build up to a faster pace &ndash; enough to get your heart beating faster than normal.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(21, 'en', 7, 'Goal 4', 4, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Replace butter or margarine with &nbsp;monounsaturated oils, for example olive oil or a spread based on olive oil.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(21, 'fr', 7, 'Objectif 4', 4, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Remplacez le beurre ou la margarine par des huiles monoinsatur&eacute;es, par exemple de l&rsquo;huile d&rsquo;olive ou un assaisonnement &agrave; base d&rsquo;huile d&rsquo;olive.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(21, 'sc', 7, 'Goal 4', 4, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Replace butter or margarine with &nbsp;monounsaturated oils, for example olive oil or a spread based on olive oil.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(22, 'en', 7, 'Goal 5', 5, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Replace white bread, rice and pasta with whole-grain versions. Cut down on your serving sizes. Try using a smaller plate or bowl.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(22, 'fr', 7, 'Objectif 5', 5, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Remplacez le pain blanc, le riz et les p&acirc;tes par leurs versions au bl&eacute; complet. Diminuez la taille de vos plats. Essayez d&rsquo;utiliser des plats ou des bols plus petits</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(22, 'sc', 7, 'Goal 5', 5, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Replace white bread, rice and pasta with whole-grain versions. Cut down on your serving sizes. Try using a smaller plate or bowl.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(23, 'en', 7, 'Set your own Goal!', 6, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
	(23, 'fr', 7, 'Crez votre propre objectif!', 6, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
	(23, 'sc', 7, 'Set your own Goal!', 6, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
	(24, 'en', 1, 'Goal 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Quit or cut down on smoking</li>\r\n	<li>See our Smoking page here</li>\r\n	<li>Get more exercise</li>\r\n	<li>Aim to be physically active every day for at least 20 minutes. See our Physical Activity page here.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(24, 'fr', 1, 'Objectif 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Arr&ecirc;tez de fumer ou ralentissez votre consommation</li>\r\n   <li>Regardez notre page Consommation de tabac ici</li>\r\n   <li>Faites plus d&rsquo;exercice physique</li>\r\n   <li>Essayez d&rsquo;&ecirc;tre physiquement actif chaque jour pendant au moins 20 minutes. Regardez notre page Activit&eacute; physique ici</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(24, 'sc', 1, 'Goal 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Quit or cut down on smoking</li>\r\n	<li>See our Smoking page here</li>\r\n	<li>Get more exercise</li>\r\n	<li>Aim to be physically active every day for at least 20 minutes. See our Physical Activity page here.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(25, 'en', 1, 'Goal 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>If you drink alcohol on a regular/daily basis, aim to cut down</li>\r\n	<li>Avoid binge drinking</li>\r\n	<li>See our Alcohol page here</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(25, 'fr', 1, 'Objectif 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Si vous buvez de l&rsquo;alcool de fa&ccedil;on r&eacute;guli&egrave;re/quotidienne, essayez de r&eacute;duire votre consommation</li>\r\n   <li>Evitez le &laquo;&nbsp;binge drinking&nbsp;&raquo;, la consommation de grandes quantit&eacute;s d&rsquo;alcool en une seule occasion</li>\r\n   <li>Regardez notre page Alcool ici</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(25, 'sc', 1, 'Goal 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>If you drink alcohol on a regular/daily basis, aim to cut down</li>\r\n	<li>Avoid binge drinking</li>\r\n	<li>See our Alcohol page here</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(26, 'en', 1, 'Goal 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Lose weight if needed</li>\r\n	<li>Aim for 1lb per week in order to maintain weight loss</li>\r\n	<li>See our <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=9">Diet</a> and <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=7">Obesity</a> pages</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(26, 'fr', 1, 'Objectif 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Perdez du poids si n&eacute;cessaire</li>\r\n   <li>Visez 500 grammes par semaine afin de maintenir la perte de poids sur la dur&eacute;e</li>\r\n   <li>Regardez nos pages <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=9">Alimentation</a> et <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=7">Ob&eacute;sit&eacute;</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(26, 'sc', 1, 'Goal 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Lose weight if needed</li>\r\n	<li>Aim for 1lb per week in order to maintain weight loss</li>\r\n	<li>See our <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=9">Diet</a> and <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=7">Obesity</a> pages</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(27, 'en', 1, 'Set your own Goal!', 4, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
	(27, 'fr', 1, 'Crez votre propre objectif!', 4, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
	(27, 'sc', 1, 'Set your own Goal!', 4, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
	(28, 'en', 5, 'Goal 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Quit Smoking!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Your local chemist will have information on the best help available</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Talk to your GP</li>\r\n	<li>Ask your family and friends for support and to join you in quitting!</li>\r\n	<li>Contact a quit smoking programme</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(28, 'fr', 5, 'Objectif 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Arr&ecirc;tez de fumer&nbsp;!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Votre pharmacien aura des informations sur les meilleures aides disponibles.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n   <li>Discutez-en avec votre m&eacute;decin traitant</li>\r\n   <li>Demandez &agrave; votre famille et &agrave; vos amis de vous aider et d&rsquo;arr&ecirc;ter de fumer eux aussi&nbsp;!</li>\r\n   <li>Contactez un programme d&rsquo;arr&ecirc;t de tabagisme</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(28, 'sc', 5, 'Goal 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Quit Smoking!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Your local chemist will have information on the best help available</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Talk to your GP</li>\r\n	<li>Ask your family and friends for support and to join you in quitting!</li>\r\n	<li>Contact a quit smoking programme</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(29, 'en', 5, 'Goal 2', 2, '\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cut down!</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(29, 'fr', 5, 'Objectif 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Diminuez votre consommation&nbsp;!</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(29, 'sc', 5, 'Goal 2', 2, '\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cut down!</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(30, 'en', 10, 'Goal 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Cut out butter and replace it with olive oil</li>\r\n	<li>Eat two pieces of fruit and three portions of vegetables a day</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>See our Diet page <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=9">here</a></p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(30, 'fr', 10, 'Objectif 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Arr&ecirc;tez le beurre, et remplacez-le par de l&rsquo;huile d&rsquo;olive</li>\r\n   <li>Mangez 2 fruits et 3 portions de l&eacute;gumes par jour</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Regardez notre page Alimentation <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=9">ici</a></p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(30, 'sc', 10, 'Goal 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Cut out butter and replace it with olive oil</li>\r\n	<li>Eat two pieces of fruit and three portions of vegetables a day</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>See our Diet page <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=9">here</a></p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(31, 'en', 10, 'Goal 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Quit smoking or cut down</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>See <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=5">here </a>for more information</p>\r\n\r\n<p>and/or</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cut down on alcohol. Stay below the recommended alcohol limit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>See our Alcohol page <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=6">here</a></p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(31, 'fr', 10, 'Objectif 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Arr&ecirc;tez de fumer ou ralentissez votre consommation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Regardez <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=5">ici</a> pour plus d&rsquo;informations</p>\r\n\r\n<p>et/ou</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n   <li>Diminuez votre consommation d&rsquo;alcool. Restez sous les limites recommand&eacute;es.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Regardez notre page Alcool <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=6">ici</a>.</p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(31, 'sc', 10, 'Goal 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Quit smoking or cut down</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>See <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=5">here </a>for more information</p>\r\n\r\n<p>and/or</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cut down on alcohol. Stay below the recommended alcohol limit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>See our Alcohol page <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=6">here</a></p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(32, 'en', 10, 'Goal 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Go for a fast walk or bicycle ride for 20 minutes four times a week</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>See our Physical Activity page <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=4">here</a></p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(32, 'fr', 10, 'Objectif 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Faites une marche rapide ou un tour en v&eacute;lo de 20 minutes, 4 fois par semaine</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Regardez notre page Activit&eacute; physique <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=4">ici</a></p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(32, 'sc', 10, 'Goal 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Go for a fast walk or bicycle ride for 20 minutes four times a week</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>See our Physical Activity page <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=4">here</a></p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(33, 'en', 10, 'Set your own Goal!', 4, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>\r\n<p>If you need to lose weight, visit our <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=4">Physical Activity</a> and <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=9">Diet </a>pages</p>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
	(33, 'fr', 10, 'Crez votre propre objectif!', 4, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>\r\n<p>If you need to lose weight, visit our <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=4">Physical Activity</a> and <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=9">Diet </a>pages</p>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
	(33, 'sc', 10, 'Set your own Goal!', 4, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>\r\n<p>If you need to lose weight, visit our <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=4">Physical Activity</a> and <a href="infos-riskfactor.html?riskfactor=9">Diet </a>pages</p>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
	(34, 'en', 2, 'Goal 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Get outdoors and walk, cycle or just spend time in the garden. Aim for 30 minutes a day</li>\r\n	<li>Eat a healthy, balanced diet and/or improve your sleep with help from our sleep tips</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(34, 'fr', 2, 'Objectif 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Sortez &agrave; l&rsquo;ext&eacute;rieur et faites de la marche, du cyclisme ou passez simplement du temps dans un jardin ou un parc. Essayez de faire cela 30 minutes par jour.</li>\r\n   <li>Ayez une alimentation saine et &eacute;quilibr&eacute;e et/ou am&eacute;liorez votre sommeil gr&acirc;ce &agrave; nos conseils sur le sommeil.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(34, 'sc', 2, 'Goal 1', 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Get outdoors and walk, cycle or just spend time in the garden. Aim for 30 minutes a day</li>\r\n	<li>Eat a healthy, balanced diet and/or improve your sleep with help from our sleep tips</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(35, 'en', 2, 'Goal 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Talk to your family and friends</li>\r\n	<li>Spend one evening a week on a social activity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Sometimes we need extra support when we feel low or depressed</p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(35, 'fr', 2, 'Objectif 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Parlez &agrave; votre famille et vos amis</li>\r\n   <li>Passez une soir&eacute;e par semaine &agrave; une activit&eacute; sociale</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Parfois nous avons besoin de soutien suppl&eacute;mentaire lorsque nous nous sentons moins bien ou d&eacute;prim&eacute;.</p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(35, 'sc', 2, 'Goal 2', 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Talk to your family and friends</li>\r\n	<li>Spend one evening a week on a social activity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Sometimes we need extra support when we feel low or depressed</p>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(36, 'en', 2, 'Goal 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Talk to your GP and ask about counselling services that are available</li>\r\n	<li>If you don&rsquo;t wish to talk to your GP, most counselling services take self-referrals. See our link below to contact a service</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(36, 'fr', 2, 'Objectif 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n   <li>Parlez &agrave; votre m&eacute;decin traitant, et demandez-lui les services d&rsquo;aide qui existent.</li>\r\n   <li>Si vous n&rsquo;avez pas envie de parler &agrave; votre m&eacute;decin traitant, la plupart des services d&rsquo;aide permettent aux patients de les contacter d&rsquo;eux-m&ecirc;mes. Regardez notre lien ci-dessous pour contacter un de ces services</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(36, 'sc', 2, 'Goal 3', 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Talk to your GP and ask about counselling services that are available</li>\r\n	<li>If you don&rsquo;t wish to talk to your GP, most counselling services take self-referrals. See our link below to contact a service</li>\r\n</ul>', 'images/goal-somethingnew.jpg'),
	(37, 'en', 2, 'Set your own Goal!', 4, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
	(37, 'fr', 2, 'Crez votre propre objectif!', 4, '<textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>', 'images/goal-ownprogram.jpg'),
